<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
ToT has nothing at all to do with mana pool. Try hunting in Guk, keep a wiz mob mezzed- you can ToT in nonstop when it pops, and youll always get the mana. Its actually mana efficient if you can time it well to sit a mezzed caster mob thatll give you full ToT mana and keep it as a ToT slave, along w/wandering mind.<P>If you really wanna test it, torment a caster mob and keep it rooted. Then test ToT on it several times; you might get a bit less if the resist roll goes high enough, but you should still get near FM.Just make sure the mob is pre-50, e.g. a kor in OS or something; since Torment has been shown to keep a mob perma-OOM once on, thatll clinch it.<P>--------------------<P>Dexanth Dragonborne<BR>60th Phantasmist of Fennin Ro
</FONT>
